    "name": "DESTROYER BURGER",
    "steam_appid": 3261200,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hey, you. You're finally awake. It's time to get up, put on your clothes, eat a bowl of sugary cereal, head out the door. You've just started working at the nearest DESTROYER BURGER, America's favorite fast food restaurant. Destroyer Burger is a fast-paced first-person fast food chaos simulator about multitasking, bad decisions, and corporate despair.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/328b45fcad8ff7104709dfd826c17985.avif?t=1770739908\" width=776 height=254 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/30f27192b1c6458edeb7deb036a3f17e.poster.avif?t=1770739908\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/30f27192b1c6458edeb7deb036a3f17e.webm?t=1770739908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/30f27192b1c6458edeb7deb036a3f17e.mp4?t=1770739908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Juggle multiple customers, learn meal combinations and kick out the most troublesome patrons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep your stocks high: prepare fries in advance, always fill up the grill, and be ready for anything.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax, the worst is yet to come. Struggle through the intensive rush hours when people overrun your little restaurant.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/ef2e2f7fd9b0f23b4177bbe3417cfc5c.avif?t=1770739908\" width=776 height=161 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/2b0f7ffba0269f545724403bdda91784.poster.avif?t=1770739908\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/2b0f7ffba0269f545724403bdda91784.webm?t=1770739908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/2b0f7ffba0269f545724403bdda91784.mp4?t=1770739908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your playthrough with over 30 different perks that improve your abilities to create meals from frozen slop.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy affordable crappy Norwegian furniture to stave off the inevitable existential crisis of working in fast food.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill the pain with various medical supplies to improve your chances at victory.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/0be2968dc51cb898200136c19c5317eb.avif?t=1770739908\" width=776 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/d3c37b6d943b8f082b1f3886a3f121d6.poster.avif?t=1770739908\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/d3c37b6d943b8f082b1f3886a3f121d6.webm?t=1770739908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/d3c37b6d943b8f082b1f3886a3f121d6.mp4?t=1770739908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features a replayable main campaign with multiple endings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also included: an advanced longer campaign and a randomizer mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's also a super-secret ending which you won't even know to look for unless you read this description ;3</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/e988016e856d12ce2946c3e841e443e3.avif?t=1770739908\" width=776 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>juuf1n:</strong>   <br>Now if someone still hasn’t wishlisted this game yet, then by all means go wishlist Destroyer Burger. This is an absolutely top-tier game. I promise.<br><br><strong>Apripsykoosi:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I feel like someone's been smacking my buns with a spatula. 10/10 would flip my sh*t again.<br><br><strong>kosminenkaaos:</strong>   <br>This game brought about my 'Nam flashbacks. And that's quite the feat because I'm a millennial. 6/5 would recommend for anyone.<br> <br><strong>maerikaroliina:</strong>   <br>Easy and fun.  <br> <br><strong>veranthia:</strong>   <br>Destroyer Burger is hectic fun! The satire doesn’t hold itself back, and the gameplay doesn’t leave you cold. Strong recommendation!  <br> <br><strong>snihy:</strong>  <br>This is really fun, it’s addictive. Stressful, but still fun — not too stressful.  <br> <br><strong>TheAsgaard:</strong>  <br>It’s fun, it’s enjoyable, it’s challenging.  <br> <br><strong>lakoninen:</strong>   <br>Destroyer Burger hilariously combines the chaos behind a fast-food counter with the journey home after a brutal workday. The game has more layers than Mallie’s monster burger. Big recommendation! <br> <br><strong>kiskoo:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is UNIQUE in many ways. You’ll be stressed out as hell but you’ll wake up tomorrow wanting to flip some more patties. Honorary mention to the depression system and all the never ending references, you’ll have a good laugh! Ps. Please remember to oil them grills…<br><br><strong>MedicFinland:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroyer Burger will pump up your blood and destroy your fate in your organizing skills. It will make you feel like you are nothing against this corporate junk food manufacturing machine. 10/10 would play again to up my blood pressure.<br><br><strong>LokkiJay:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Hey, this is going pretty well&quot; is something you should not think while playing Destroyer Burger, as things can and will get out of hand. A very well-made game with satisfying progression and loop, filled to the brim with humor catering to my questionable tastes!<br><br><strong>BasicPena:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroyer Burger is fun, relaxing and hectic at the same time, accompanied by sweet music.<br><br><strong>Keskiviikkoilta:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Highly recommend if you enjoy chaos, challenge, and laughing at your own mistakes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/a9bdb6bdaccd51791ba449a0ae30df38.avif?t=1770739908\" width=776 height=234 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/634ccade7309bb45f471a5fe1eb2817e.poster.avif?t=1770739908\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/634ccade7309bb45f471a5fe1eb2817e.webm?t=1770739908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/634ccade7309bb45f471a5fe1eb2817e.mp4?t=1770739908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple gameplay modes with escalating difficulty and systemic chaos.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes 3D acceleration technology (warning: requires a GPU).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save your progress with a revolutionary new feature called “save your game”.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be able to quit the game without pressing Alt+F4.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Possibly the only game on Steam that has earnable achievements (we didn't check).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/c00936d0569198aa4a5cd6d843aa6e41.avif?t=1770739908\" width=776 height=311 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/94b8e93b248b1f68f9fa784f8340ce50.poster.avif?t=1770739908\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/94b8e93b248b1f68f9fa784f8340ce50.webm?t=1770739908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261200/extras/94b8e93b248b1f68f9fa784f8340ce50.mp4?t=1770739908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
